| builder for Acorn/ROOL DDE
| By Paolo Fabio Zaino

| Some useful build configuration bits:
Set Build$Clean 1

| Temporarly set this directory as root
Set Return$Dir &
Dir <Obey$Dir>

| Make the Library
WimpSlot -min 1024k

If <Build$Clean> = 1 Then wipe o.* ~C F

amu THROWBACK=-throwback -f MakeFileDDE

| Reset
dir <Return$Dir>
Unset Return$Dir
